<plot>The rich businessman Orhan has an unhappy marriage, he spends most of his time with his little son. After a big fight with his wife Sermin, he leaves home. One day at a bar he meets a singer named Leyla. They are attracted to each other. Hiding from her that he is married, Orhan asks Leyla to join him for a trip to Antalya. They have a splendid time together. However when Leyla finds out about his marriage, she leaves him. For Orhan happy days are over.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?664369</url></doc>
